<ab facs="#facs_144_r1l14">walds <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc / das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr 
